        <add place="superlinear"> he was</add>
      </mod> descended <lb n="c57-0023_main_8"/>of a good family in France and had but recently <lb n="c57-0023_main_9"/>left his country when he been deprived of <lb n="c57-0023_main_10"/>a competent fortune which he <mod>
